%help
    Calls a python script that imports pysam and splits the multiplexed .bam file into
    individual .bam files per cell.

    Usage
    -----

    ./00_split_bam_SS3.sif <path/to/bam/> <path/to/barcode/dataframe.csv> <path/to/output/>

    See ./00_split_bam_SS3.sif --help for more info.
